// base 456332
// defineOption_1(0,'','');
// option description t_long_string to t_short_string: no change
// reduce ptr^.defineOption(): 100 bytes per call
// reduce customer type handler: 1500bytes per handler based on bmschargestate

// gSystem: move to pointers = 455700, not much change as not much duplication

// v5: 453712 gSystem is not pointers but in code space
// 454584: derive EC classes for monitor and parse, 400bytes each
